ğŸ“‚ 3ï¸âƒ£ Project Architecture Structure

We implemented a feature-based modular structure, instead of a flat layer structure.

Base Package:
com.pranav.financetracker

Feature-Based Structure:
auth/
user/
category/
expense/
group/
split/
settlement/
friend/
savings/
budget/
analytics/
email/
scheduler/
config/
common/


Each feature will contain:

controller/

service/

repository/

entity/

dto/

Why Feature-Based?

Scalable for large systems

Easier maintenance

Clear domain separation

Industry-level architecture

ğŸ³ 4ï¸âƒ£ Database Containerization

PostgreSQL was containerized using Docker.

docker-compose.yml created at project root.

Configuration includes:

PostgreSQL 15 image

Database: finance_tracker

Username: postgres

Password: postgres

Persistent volume for data

Database started using:

docker compose up -d


This ensures:

No local DB installation required

Reproducible environment

Easy future deployment

